                  <p>
                      It is Canadian Association for Girls in Science’s policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect while operating our<br />
                      website. This Privacy Policy applies to GirlsInScience.ca (hereinafter, “us”, “we”, or “GirlsInScience.ca”). We respect your privacy and are committed<br />
