                  <p>
                      GirlsInScience.ca uses the remarketing services to advertise on third party websites (including Google) to previous visitors to our site. It could<br />
                      mean that we advertise to previous visitors who haven’t completed a task on our site, for example using the contact form to make an enquiry. This<br />
