                      You can set preferences for how Google advertises to you using the Google Ad Preferences page, and if you want to you can opt out of interest-<br />
                      based advertising entirely by cookie settings or permanently using a browser plugin.
                  </p><br />
                  <b>– Protection of Certain Personally-Identifying Information</b>
                  <p>
                      Canadian Association for Girls in Science discloses potentially personally-identifying and personally-identifying information only to those of its<br />
                      employees, contractors and affiliated organizations that (i) need to know that information in order to process it on Canadian Association for Girls<br />
                      in Science’s behalf or to provide services available at Canadian Association for Girls in Science’s website, and (ii) that have agreed not to disclose it<br />
                      to others. Some of those employees, contractors and affiliated organizations may be located outside of your home country; by using Canadian<br />
                      Association for Girls in Science’s website, you consent to the transfer of such information to them. Canadian Association for Girls in Science will<br />
                      not rent or sell potentially personally-identifying and personally-identifying information to anyone. Other than to its employees, contractors and<br />
                      affiliated organizations, as described above, Canadian Association for Girls in Science discloses potentially personally-identifying and personally-<br />
                      identifying information only in response to a subpoena, court order or other governmental request, or when Canadian Association for Girls in<br />
                      Science believes in good faith that disclosure is reasonably necessary to protect the property or rights of Canadian Association for Girls in Science,<br />
                      third parties or the public at large.<br />
