                  <p>
                      Canadian Association for Girls in Science may collect statistics about the behaviour of visitors to its website. Canadian Association for Girls in<br />
                      Science may display this information publicly or provide it to others. However, Canadian Association for Girls in Science does not disclose your<br />
                      personally-identifying information.
                  </p><br />
                  <b>- Cookies</b>
                  <p>
                      To enrich and perfect your online experience, Canadian Association for Girls in Science uses “Cookies”, similar technologies and services provided<br />
                      by others to display personalized content, appropriate advertising and store your preferences on your computer.<br />
                      A cookie is a string of information that a website stores on a visitor’s computer, and that the visitor’s browser provides to the website each time<br />
                      the visitor returns. Canadian Association for Girls in Science uses cookies to help Canadian Association for Girls in Science identify and track<br />
                      visitors, their usage of http://GirlsInScience.ca, and their website access preferences. Canadian Association for Girls in Science visitors who do not<br />
                      wish to have cookies placed on their computers should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using Canadian Association for Girls in<br />
                      Science’s websites, with the drawback that certain features of Canadian Association for Girls in Science’s websites may not function properly<br />
                      without the aid of cookies.<br />
                      By continuing to navigate our website without changing your cookie settings, you hereby acknowledge and agree to Canadian Association for Girls<br />
                      in Science’s use of cookies.
                  </p><br />
